The current price remains unchanged: the equivalent of 140 dollars for a tourist visa, 150 dollars for Visa with application (including Visa for time workers) and 390 dollars for hands and investors.
Those who only want to extend their visa must not have a conversation in the consulate, they must only present themselves to the next ASC, where they present their documents and fingerprints.
As biometric data are collected in the ASC, applicants who need a second deadline for the conversation in the consulate remain there less time than before.
